data.description: Horses allowed!!! Great flat lot.  Beautiful 9 yr old 4 bed, 3.5 bath home with approx 3300 sq ft of living space on over 2 acres.  Beautiful hardwoods on first floor (need some refinishing, seller will offer $10,000 credit for floors and paint upstairs). Beautiful gourmet kitchen with SS appliances, granite and island, dining room, breakfast area, office and family room on first floor.   Spacious master suite with beautiful private bath,  large soaking tub upstairs.  Three additional bedrooms, full bath and large laundry room finish out the second floor.   The downstairs is a  knock-out finished walk out lower level  which has large sliding doors to the backyard, full bath and plenty of space to entertain. Could potentially be used as an in law suite, buyer to verify with county. There is plenty of room out back for the kids and critters to run! Close to Rt 1 and I-95, waterfront dining,  Approx 1 hr to Phila Airport and 40 min to BWI. Live in the country but close to everything! No HoA.  The home has solar panels which are leased.
